{"tid":2330272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣空軍全面加強警告射擊演練 應對中共軍機持續擾台而可能發生的衝突","createTime":"2020-12-18T01:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T07:30:26.000Z","uid":292499,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"84c8cbba4593d6add7e828b4bbf97564b3024051","tid":2330272,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:01:26.000Z","msg":"資深飛行員透露，從12月上旬開始，包括嘉義、花蓮、清泉崗、新竹、台南及馬公等基地，已要求二機編隊訓練做起，由領隊視各種情況實施「警告射擊演練」，基本上操作「警告射擊演練」科目不難，合格的飛行員對全程動作都很純熟，但使用時機的判斷就很重要，態度也要很嚴謹，如領隊如何解讀、因應戰管所下達的警告射擊命令？對僚機如何下達射擊指示？及命令下達時機等，主要考量為狀況緊急時，心理因素及抗壓性對飛行員是很大的考驗，因此類似的演練是否純熟就益顯重要。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n資深退役飛行員指出，目前空軍各基地的作法，每次升空警戒或監控共機，都會挑選由成熟、資深飛行員擔任領隊，避免擦槍走火情況發生，但因為上從上將空軍司令，下至中尉飛行員，迄今無人有過這種開砲警告射擊的經驗，一旦碰上了，領隊的心理素質和臨機判斷，不但是一大考驗，也是任務是否成功的關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3384834\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3384834&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=bc053a5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3384834&h=7800ea32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3384834</a>"},{"pid":"210e4009b6fd2ada60c9e45e02d18c991f6a6ecb","tid":2330272,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:01:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b7007bb1355f446266b49aa13959d9c73cdcb7","tid":2330272,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img